{"tid":1631352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[五毛名單整合] [勿中政府詭計］","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:54.000Z","uid":162711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a64185f4398f982c37e1a5aac993bed31a2daad9","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"1. 帶風向鼓吹人亂尻咁裝修/獅鳥/<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">搞人地宗教</span>/作出一切無理嘅激進行為，利用勇武手足憤怒嘅情緒同埋勇氣，目的就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>將和勇分化</strong></span></span>，企圖抹黑勇武，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚇鳩啲淺黃同中立派</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有啲就企圖鼓吹叫人打陣地戰，呢啲真係要小心，因為個後果就係俾狗拉，返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n2.係又屌唔係又屌，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最鍾意就係屌鳩啲和理非</span></span></strong>  又話和理非民意撚，我梗係唔係care班藍屍，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>而係care中立派/淺黃淺藍/一班爹哋媽咪銀髮族</strong></span></span>。或者屌鳩啲遊行集中撚，唔排除鼓吹集中撚嗰班有一部份係鬼，但係都有好大部份人唔係，係咁屌都冇意思㗎啦，只可以話做法不完美，可接受，需要改善<br />\n<br />\n但呢班友係又屌唔係又屌，其實就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想撩交嗌，分化連登手足</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3.做乜柒都話核爆都唔割<br />\n<br />\n班風向撚就係想利用我哋當初嘅宗旨: 不割蓆，不薦灰，不分化，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>企圖合理化一切走火入魔嘅行為</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你真係手足，我相信你會好樂意聆聽我哋嘅意見，唔會堅持帶風向/堅持激進落去。即使我哋係和理非，冇勇氣打狗，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>至少我哋時刻保持警覺同理智</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你係風向撚，你已經好有可能係鬼，fact check 咗之後，Sorry 我地要割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布: 有以上特徵嘅，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一律有可能係鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如有遺漏，請各位手足喺下面補充<br />\n<br />\n香港人要團結啊，不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時刻警覺五毛嘅出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b099cab0e16d6afaa6af44d4275250f22610629","tid":1631352,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3ba549e6f782c06c93986e023d1b6c6b89cf687","tid":1631352,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"41637c28b416e77833fb2304025342c5e24d511d","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30c530585296d8de682d96838c5aaf2c8416ff9c","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"5731f5d8ceaa51e63ebbf3ae6497486275cf7b19","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c90281a0060bd7139fc24cdf66aec1452ee5b9be","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"384f9200f7201154305b5021d49ae4a26b6b9833","tid":1631352,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"e366b73fe4b85b3c3138f258526dbe4b11cae2f2","tid":1631352,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4171b1c944e748d7e28bf75f97b2503b42287861","tid":163